Pump Installation & Commissioning

Irrigation Systems

Automation & Remote Monitoring

GSM pump controllers, level monitors and multi-tank automation for homes and farms. Smart water management, made accessible.

The Founder

கோவிந்தராஜன் — The Farmer's Guide

A Tamil poet and civic activist who believed that serving others was purpose enough. In 1972, he proposed free electricity for farmers to the Agriculture Minister — and saw it become policy. He didn't open a pump shop. He opened a centre. உழவர் மையம் was his declaration of purpose.

"என் பங்குக்கு நான் ஒரு வழிகாட்டி என்பதில் பெருமைபடுகிறேன்."

— கோவிந்தராஜன், உழவர் மையன்
